    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The undersurfaces of shoes that elevate the foot at approximately the same height over their entire length. These may be solid or constructed from discontinuous components such as stilts or wedges.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
